cat << EOF
This client is a program to configure the daemon PBButtons with a comfortable GUI. It works with all PBButtonsd 
daemons v0.5.0+. PowerPrefs was nearly completly rewritten and ported to GTK+ 2.0.

Any configuration change becomes active until the 'set' button is pressed. Up to this point any change could be 
canceled with the 'dischard' button.
EOF
